				<tr>
					<td valign="top" colspan="2" class="value"><span class="title">Valeur</span></td>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<td><p>L'une des constantes suivantes: <span class="literal">collapse</span> | <span class="literal">hidden</span> | <span class="literal">inherit</span> | <span class="literal">visible</span>. IE pour Windows ne reconna&icirc;t pas la valeur <span class="literal">collapse</span>. Navigator 4 autorise uniquement l'attribut visibility pour les &eacute;l&eacute;ments positionn&eacute;s.</p>
					</td>
				</tr>
